title: Geospatial Visualization on Bike Routes in Boston
description: Created an interactive visualization of Boston's BlueBikes system using D3.js and Mapbox. The project displays bike station traffic patterns, with circle sizes indicating total trips and colors showing the balance between arrivals and departures. Features include time-based filtering and bike route overlays for both Boston and Cambridge areas.
